本周谁离开了“叛徒”？ https://www.nme.com/news/tv/who-left-the-traitors-this-week-season-2-3568657?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=who-left-the-traitors-this-week-第2季Adam StarkeyWed, 10 Jan 2024 22:20:22 +0000 NewsTV NewsBBC https://www.nme.com/?p=3568657 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="叛徒们" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前方剧透</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/who-left-the-traitors-this-week-season-2-3568657">本周谁离开了“叛徒”？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="叛徒们" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/traitors-season-2-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>《叛徒》</em></a>已成为过去十年中最出色的真人秀节目之一。</p><p>该系列赛由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼 (Claudia Winkleman) 主持，22 名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡内争夺高达 12 万英镑的奖金。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-two-contestants-whos-in-cast-what-do-we-know-3564637">《叛徒》第二季参赛者：演员阵容中有哪些以及我们对他们了解多少？</a></strong></li></ul><p>当他们到达城堡时，一小部分人被选为“叛徒”，他们必须消灭“忠实”参赛者才能获得奖品。然而，如果后者能够通过每日圆桌会议找出并驱逐欺骗性的参赛者，他们就会赢得现金奖励。</p><p>继 2022 年首季取得突破后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/bbc">BBC</a>续订了第二季和第三季。</p><h2>到目前为止，第二季中谁离开了<em>叛徒队</em>？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3564673" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564673" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564673" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Aubrey-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564673" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的奥布里。图片来源：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p><strong>奥布里</strong></p><p>今年系列中第一个被谋杀的人是奥布里，因为他的观察力和洞察力吓坏了叛徒。 </p><figure id="attachment_3564655" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564655" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564655" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sonja-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564655" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的索尼娅。图片来源：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p><strong>索尼娅</strong></p><p>奥布里被谋杀后，索尼娅在本赛季的第一场圆桌会议上被驱逐。由于她在猜测叛徒的身份方面可能过于直率，该小组对她产生了怀疑。然而，她是一名忠实信徒。 </p><figure id="attachment_3564660" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564660" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564660" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Kyra-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564660" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的凯拉。图片来源：英国广播公司</figcaption></figure><p><strong>凯拉</strong></p><p>在第三集中，凯拉在第一次圆桌会议上证明自己是一个强有力、有说服力的声音后被谋杀。 </p><figure id="attachment_3564656" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564656" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564656" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Brian-traitors.jpg" alt="布莱恩叛徒" width="2000" height="